---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Slash Commands — GitHub Copilot CLI Handbook"
  description="Interactive commands you can type in GitHub Copilot CLI"
>
  <article class="handbook-content">
    <header class="page-intro">
      <h1>Slash Commands</h1>
      <p>Interactive commands you type in the CLI, starting with <code>/</code></p>
    </header>

    <h2>Session Management</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/resume</code> — Continue previous sessions (v0.0.386, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/clear</code> — Start a new session</li>
      <li><code>/new</code> — Alias for <code>/clear</code> (v0.0.381, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/rename</code> — Rename current session (v0.0.392, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/session rename</code> — Rename current session</li>
      <li><code>/share</code> — Save session as markdown file or GitHub gist (v0.0.359, Nov 2025)</li>
      <li><code>/compact</code> — Trigger session compaction manually (v0.0.374, Jan 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Model and Settings</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/model</code> — Change the model interactively or with <code>/model &lt;model&gt;</code> (v0.0.329, Sep 2025)</li>
      <li><code>/models</code> — Alias for <code>/model</code> (v0.0.389, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/theme</code> — Switch themes with GitHub Dark/Light (v0.0.400, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/on-air</code> — Hide model names and quota details for streaming (v0.0.407, Feb 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/streamer-mode</code> — Hide preview model names and quota details (v0.0.408, Feb 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Code Review and Changes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/diff</code> — Review session changes (v0.0.399, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/review</code> — Analyze code changes (v0.0.388, Jan 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Context and Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/context</code> — Visualize token usage (v0.0.372, Dec 2025)</li>
      <li><code>/usage</code> — View premium request usage, session time, code changes, and per-model token stats (v0.0.333, Oct 2025)</li>
      <li><code>/changelog</code> — View release notes (v0.0.406, Feb 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/help</code> — CLI agent can read its own help to answer capability questions (v0.0.355, Nov 2025)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Working Directory</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/cwd</code> — Change working directory</li>
      <li><code>/cd</code> — Alias for <code>/cwd</code> (v0.0.384, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/add-dir</code> — Add directory to context</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Agent and Task Management</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/agent</code> — Invoke custom agents (v0.0.353, Oct 2025)</li>
      <li><code>/delegate</code> — Delegate a task asynchronously to Copilot coding agent (v0.0.353, Oct 2025)</li>
      <li><code>/tasks</code> — View and manage background tasks (v0.0.404, Feb 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Plugins and Extensions</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/plugin</code> — Plugin marketplace management (v0.0.392, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/plugin install</code> — Install plugins from GitHub repos, URLs, and local paths (v0.0.396, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/plugin update</code> — Update installed plugins (v0.0.392, Jan 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>MCP Server Management</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/mcp add</code> — Add MCP servers (v0.0.339, Oct 2025)</li>
      <li><code>/mcp show</code> — Display all configured MCP servers (v0.0.395, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/mcp show &lt;server-name&gt;</code> — Display server details and available tools (v0.0.397, Jan 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions and Configuration</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/instructions</code> — View and toggle custom instruction files (v0.0.407, Feb 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/init</code> — Generate Copilot instructions (v0.0.396, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/init suppress</code> — Control init suggestions per repository (v0.0.410, Feb 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Experimental Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/experimental</code> — Show help screen listing experimental features (v0.0.405, Feb 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Permissions</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/allow-all</code> — Auto-approve all permissions during a session (v0.0.399, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>/yolo</code> — Auto-approve all permissions during a session (v0.0.399, Jan 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>IDE Integration</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/ide</code> — CLI integrates with VS Code (v0.0.409, Feb 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Terminal Setup</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/terminal-setup</code> — Set up multi-line input on terminals (v0.0.341, Oct 2025)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Exit Commands</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>/exit</code> — Exit the CLI</li>
      <li><code>/quit</code> — Alias for <code>/exit</code> (v0.0.349, Oct 2025)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Special Input Methods</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><code>!</code> — Execute shell commands directly (v0.0.333, Oct 2025)</li>
      <li><code>&</code> — Prefix shortcut for delegating prompts to run in background (v0.0.384, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li><code>?</code> — Quick help overlay with grouped shortcuts and commands (v0.0.409, Feb 2026)</li>
      <li>Ctrl+X then <code>/</code> — Run slash commands without losing your input (v0.0.399, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li>Ctrl+P — Runs slash commands while preserving input (v0.0.407, Feb 2026)</li>
      <li>Ctrl+D — Queue slash commands alongside messages (v0.0.394, Jan 2026)</li>
      <li>Ctrl+Q — Queue messages for later (replaces Ctrl+D queueing) (v0.0.407, Feb 2026)</li>
    </ul>

    <hr>
    <p><small>Source: <a href="https://github.com/github/copilot-cli/releases" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">github/copilot-cli/releases</a> · Last updated: February 2026</small></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
